            <div class="SCXW126874900 BCX8">
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW126874900 BCX8">
<h3 class="Paragraph SCXW126874900 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;"><span class="TextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8">As Etapas da Inova&ccedil;&atilde;o</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW126874900 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></h3>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW126874900 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW126874900 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span>No </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW126874900 BCX8">Avantt.i</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8">, entendemos que o processo de inova&ccedil;&atilde;o, seja para produtos, servi&ccedil;os ou o pr&oacute;prio neg&oacute;cio, envolve algumas etapas principais: a VIS&Atilde;O, que orienta os esfor&ccedil;os; a CRIA&Ccedil;&Atilde;O, que gera v&aacute;rias rotas a seguir; e a EXECU&Ccedil;&Atilde;O, baseada em t&eacute;cnicas de implementa&ccedil;&atilde;o de projetos de inova&ccedil;&atilde;o. Esses esfor&ccedil;os visam entregar um RESULTADO esperado.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW126874900 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW126874900 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW126874900 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span>De maneira simplificada, todas as empresas passam por essas etapas, seja de forma estruturada, simult&acirc;nea ou desordenada. Nosso objetivo aqui &eacute; explorar a interse&ccedil;&atilde;o entre as etapas de cria&ccedil;&atilde;o e execu&ccedil;&atilde;o, onde ocorrem a valida&ccedil;&atilde;o e os testes. Considerando que "uma inova&ccedil;&atilde;o, no sentido econ&ocirc;mico, s&oacute; &eacute; completa quando h&aacute; uma transa&ccedil;&atilde;o comercial envolvendo uma inven&ccedil;&atilde;o", podemos afirmar que a inova&ccedil;&atilde;o deve gerar valor para algu&eacute;m. Assim, ela tem mais chances de sucesso quando tratada como um processo cient&iacute;fico, onde hip&oacute;teses s&atilde;o criadas com base em nossas cren&ccedil;as de desejabilidade e viabilidade t&eacute;cnica e econ&ocirc;mica. Se validadas ou invalidadas, essas hip&oacute;teses confirmam ou rejeitam a solu&ccedil;&atilde;o adotada.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW126874900 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW126874900 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW126874900 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span>A valida&ccedil;&atilde;o &eacute; essencial em um processo que precisa lidar com riscos e incertezas constantemente. An&aacute;lises criteriosas de poss&iacute;veis solu&ccedil;&otilde;es podem poupar esfor&ccedil;os valiosos, ajudar na prioriza&ccedil;&atilde;o de recursos e permitir decis&otilde;es mais r&aacute;pidas e corretas para o crescimento do neg&oacute;cio.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW126874900 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW126874900 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<h3 class="Paragraph SCXW126874900 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8">O Processo de </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8">v</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8">alida&ccedil;&atilde;o</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW126874900 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></h3>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW126874900 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW126874900 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span>Em um processo de valida&ccedil;&atilde;o, &eacute; necess&aacute;rio come&ccedil;ar pelas hip&oacute;teses. Ao escolher seguir por uma ideia ap&oacute;s sua cria&ccedil;&atilde;o, &eacute; preciso dar um salto de f&eacute;, ou seja, mesmo baseados em estudos e pesquisas, assumimos algumas cren&ccedil;as como verdades, mesmo que ainda carreguem incertezas. Por exemplo, a pr&aacute;tica de esportes &eacute; uma tend&ecirc;ncia, e a preocupa&ccedil;&atilde;o com a sa&uacute;de &eacute; crescente. A </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW126874900 BCX8">Jundu</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8"> teve que assumir que essas pessoas gostariam e usariam quadras de esportes de areia, o que foi um salto de f&eacute; inicial posteriormente validado.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW126874900 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW126874900 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW126874900 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span>Para validar esses saltos de f&eacute;, desenvolvemos hip&oacute;teses, que podem ser divididas em tr&ecirc;s principais tipos:</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW126874900 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW126874900 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<ul class="BulletListStyle1 SCXW126874900 BCX8" role="list">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW126874900 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="23" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW126874900 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8">Hip&oacute;teses de Desejabilidade</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8">: Algu&eacute;m quer o que estamos oferecendo? Pagariam ou dedicariam tempo para usar isso?</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW126874900 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW126874900 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<ul class="BulletListStyle1 SCXW126874900 BCX8" role="list">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW126874900 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="23" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="2" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW126874900 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8">Hip&oacute;teses de Viabilidade T&eacute;cnica</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8">: Somos capazes de produzir e criar em escala o que oferecemos? Temos recursos e parceiros para isso? Conseguimos executar os processos necess&aacute;rios?</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW126874900 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW126874900 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<ul class="BulletListStyle1 SCXW126874900 BCX8" role="list">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW126874900 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="23" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="3" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW126874900 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8">Hip&oacute;teses de Viabilidade Econ&ocirc;mica</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8">: A conta fecha? Conseguimos gerar resultado positivo?</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW126874900 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW126874900 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW126874900 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8">Pensando em um </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW126874900 BCX8">canvas</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8"> de modelo de neg&oacute;cios, podemos posicionar essas hip&oacute;teses validando diferentes &aacute;reas do neg&oacute;cio.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW126874900 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW126874900 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<h3 class="Paragraph SCXW126874900 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8">As </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8">h</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8">ip&oacute;teses de </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8">n</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8">eg&oacute;cios</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW126874900 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></h3>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW126874900 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW126874900 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span>Para definir as hip&oacute;teses, &eacute; preciso entender quais s&atilde;o nossas premissas, perguntas e cren&ccedil;as ainda n&atilde;o comprovadas. Cada hip&oacute;tese deve ser:</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW126874900 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW126874900 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<ul class="BulletListStyle1 SCXW126874900 BCX8" role="list">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW126874900 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="24" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW126874900 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8">Test&aacute;vel</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8">: Pode ser comprovada verdadeira ou falsa mediante alguma evid&ecirc;ncia.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW126874900 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW126874900 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<ul class="BulletListStyle1 SCXW126874900 BCX8" role="list">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW126874900 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="24" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="2" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW126874900 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8">Precisa</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8">: Deve ter indicadores num&eacute;ricos que apontem seu sucesso ou insucesso.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW126874900 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW126874900 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<ul class="BulletListStyle1 SCXW126874900 BCX8" role="list">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW126874900 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="24" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="3" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW126874900 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8">Distinta</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8">: Testar e validar apenas um aspecto investigado.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW126874900 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW126874900 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW126874900 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span>Com boas hip&oacute;teses definidas, os experimentos devem ser criados e alinhados entre os respons&aacute;veis, desde prot&oacute;tipos simples at&eacute; </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW126874900 BCX8">MVPs</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8"> mais elaborados. A fase de experimenta&ccedil;&atilde;o deve desenvolver testes que custem o m&iacute;nimo poss&iacute;vel para validar ou invalidar as hip&oacute;teses de maneira fiel. &Eacute; crucial analisar os experimentos adotados para que o processo de valida&ccedil;&atilde;o n&atilde;o fique estagnado nessa etapa. A import&acirc;ncia das hip&oacute;teses e a for&ccedil;a das evid&ecirc;ncias geradas precisam justificar a complexidade e os custos dos experimentos.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW126874900 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW126874900 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<h3 class="Paragraph SCXW126874900 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8">Tipos de </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8">e</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8">xperimentos</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW126874900 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></h3>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW126874900 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW126874900 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span>H&aacute; muitos tipos poss&iacute;veis de experimentos, como entrevistas com consumidores, cartas de inten&ccedil;&atilde;o de compra, </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW126874900 BCX8">crowdfunding</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8">, landing </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW126874900 BCX8">pages</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8">, impress&atilde;o 3D, campanhas de e-mail, entrevistas com parceiros e fornecedores, entre outros. O desafio &eacute; encontrar os que mais se adequam &agrave;s suas hip&oacute;teses, rod&aacute;-los e medi-los.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW126874900 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="SCXW126874900 BCX8">
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW126874900 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW126874900 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span>Um bom experimento deve responder &agrave;s seguintes perguntas:</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW126874900 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW126874900 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<ul class="BulletListStyle1 SCXW126874900 BCX8" role="list">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW126874900 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="25" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW126874900 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8">Prop&oacute;sito</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8">: O experimento foca em uma a&ccedil;&atilde;o espec&iacute;fica do neg&oacute;cio? O que esperamos aprender ou validar com ele?</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW126874900 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
