<p class="Paragraph SCXW126874900 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8">Capacidade</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8">: Qual o tamanho do experimento? Temos capacidade de conduzi-lo pelo tempo necess&aacute;rio?</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW126874900 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW126874900 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
