<p class="Paragraph SCXW126874900 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8">Valor</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW126874900 BCX8">: O experimento testa mercados e p&uacute;blicos relevantes? Existe um plano para rolar a solu&ccedil;&atilde;o se validada?</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW126874900 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
